      "span_text": "Other studies using different experimental paradigms support the idea that enhanced D, DA receptor binding does not mediate apomorphine-induced rotational behavior. examined the D, DA receptor upregulation that occurs following a unilateral substantia nigra lesion in conjunction with the upregulation that occurs following chronic treat-ment with D, antagonists."
